"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"[Zora](https://twitter.com/ourzora) is about to launch their new protocol, which aims to improve on the ERC721 token standard. One of its new features is the coupling of a market contract to an NFT. This means that every zNFT (Zora NFT) has a canonical marketplace for trading. This solves the problem of fragmented liquidity for the trading of NFTs. \\n\\nBy \\\"fragmented liquidity\\\", I'm referring to the problem where there isn't a single, logical place to go to buy an NFT (e.g. digital art), and so trading happens in a number of different storefronts. This leads to a number of inefficiencies! If everyone were just trading in the same marketplace, then you could deploy a single contract for *each NFT type*, and have everyone trade on very efficient layer-2s, *and* have it all conform to the same metadata standards.\\n\\nWe (the team at Mirror) proposed to Zora that we build a crowdfunding contract for NFTs, and integration with their protocol. I wrote up a prototype smart contract for this purpose, which you can view [here](https://gist.github.com/graemecode/0811326589450829ccd0641e8a5408d7).\\n\\nThe flow is summarized in the following diagram, and I also walked through the contract on today's livestream on YouTube ([link](https://youtu.be/9MDypeN64hQ?t=1884)).\\n\\n![Crowdfunding an NFT](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/794a8fa5-83d8-4b88-aedf-b77545b4002b.jpeg?height=1504&width=1348)\",\"timestamp\":1611373569,\"title\":\"Crowdfunding NFTs with Zora\",\"publication\":\"g\"},\"digest\":\"ZEnTCzTv3QJ5gcRy9Eh6bgOcVp3_mD4sSC_vZqGcSqM\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xCC65fA278B917042822538c44ba10AD646824026\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"jY9ZjZ3PVT5GZSOT2MQV89_EfuZGx6o0ZiERgWf2vmI\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"2DyUTrSxyPC0wHE4ltlnwbHs7y8f4ZB0n-CkGfYfkBA\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"teH6F9fJ6EP28A-fT9Vjs0Tv424sE5VtcXnpiCCXuiIbY1p7S737bj1sqP5Z0sMhTIYtDI4tJS1SX7_me-RMVA\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xdd3e66eb8082aa09d2ebb2a5492080dccb02db56bddf972bf17d537f84b53cf15db3e950031cce6e6791a7d21c419c401daa570221f583489f6d7308019422771c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize the publication of articles on g.mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"jY9ZjZ3PVT5GZSOT2MQV89_EfuZGx6o0ZiERgWf2vmI\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"2DyUTrSxyPC0wHE4ltlnwbHs7y8f4ZB0n-CkGfYfkBA\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"ZEnTCzTv3QJ5gcRy9Eh6bgOcVp3_mD4sSC_vZqGcSqM\"}"